      "skill_repair_armor"
    ],
    "faq": [
      {
        "q_cn": "通过【缮甲】弃置手牌中的装备牌，是否也计入失去过装备区里的牌数？",
        "a_cn": "不计入。只有从装备区里失去的牌才会使X减少，手牌中直接弃置的装备牌不算。",
        "q_en": "If I discard an Equipment Card from my hand via Repair Armor, does it count toward the Equipment Zone loss total?",
        "a_en": "No. Only cards lost directly from your Equipment Zone reduce X. Equipment Cards discarded from your hand do not count."
      },
      {
        "q_cn": "视为使用的【杀】是否有距离限制？",
        "a_cn": "有。视为使用的【杀】需要检测距离。",
        "q_en": "Does the [Kill] used via Repair Armor have a distance restriction?",
        "a_en": "Yes. The [Kill] used by this method is subject to normal distance checks."
      },
      {
        "q_cn": "主动替换装备或被他人弃置装备区里的牌，是否算失去过装备区里的牌？",
        "a_cn": "是的，任何方式导致装备区里的牌离开装备区，均算失去过装备区里的牌。",
        "q_en": "Does replacing an equipped card or having an equipped card discarded by another character count as losing an Equipment Zone card?",
        "a_en": "Yes. Any method that causes a card to leave your Equipment Zone counts as losing an Equipment Zone card."
      }
    ]
  }
